nodes.text: Gradress Nall was a bounty hunter who was a member of the House Salaktori chapter of the Bounty Hunters' Guild.

Nall, a third generation Salaktori hunter, was known as an arrogant, headstrong bounty hunter, who was unpopular amongst his peers. Nevertheless, Nall was gifted and dependable, with the potential to be amongst the best of his profession.
